## Technical Decisions

### Real-time Strategy
- **Decision:** Short polling (via SWR) for MVP
- **Reasoning:** Reduces infrastructure complexity while maintaining acceptable UX
- **Implementation:**
  - Active Chat: Poll every 3 seconds
  - Inbox List: Poll every 10 seconds
- **Future:** Can migrate to WebSocket/Pusher when scale demands

### Paid Messages (PPV)
- Flow: Creator sets price → Message locked → Fan purchases → Content unlocked
- Security: API strictly enforces locked content never sent until purchased
- Transaction: Creates transaction record and PPV purchase record

### Media in Messages
- **Status:** Placeholder implemented
- **Future:** Will integrate with media upload service

